Branch naming:
  feature/academy-course-cards
  fix/otp-rate-limit
  chore/update-dependencies

Commit format:
  feat: add course enrollment endpoint
  fix: resolve OTP expiry check
  chore: update Resend package
  docs: add API documentation

Review rules:
  - 1 approval required for feature branches
  - 2 approvals required for anything touching auth/
  - Sheddy must approve anything in CODEOWNERS
  - No self-merges
  - CI must pass